title: Breakfast Egg
author: jimmythelynx
description:
Breakfast Egg 1.0
No more simple egg shapes! Tilt the egg around and watch the yolk changing its rather esoteric colors. Figure out who’s made the egg and how it should look to decide whether you YUM the egg or YUK it away!
